                                <div class="timeline-body">
                                    <p class="text-muted">Invitees can propose agenda items. This gives more power to the meeting body and gives the meeting organizer the opportunity to hear about unprecendented issues.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="timeline-inverted">
                            <div class="timeline-image">
                                <%= image_tag('administration1.png', class: "img-circle img-responsive") %>
                            </div>
                            <div class="timeline-panel">
                                <div class="timeline-heading">
                                    <h4>After</h4>
                                    <h4 class="subheading">Remember what happened.</h4>
                                </div>
                                <div class="timeline-body">
                                    <p class="text-muted">Have access to an archive outlining your meeting. Use this as a reference to jog your memory and hold others accountable.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="timeline-inverted">
                            <div class="timeline-image last-bubble">
                                <h4>Be Part
                                    <br>Of Our
